  scType: 0
  scDesc: 'Shoots a slow, huge, bullet-destroying orb at the nearest enemy, exploding
    and dealing 1 HP damage to all enemies in a moderate AoE on contact, clearing
    all bullets caught in it.


    (*) Elemental Overload: The orb becomes larger,
    lasts longer, and moves slower.'
  scCommentary: Technically you can outrun the ball. Or just, sidestep it if you're
    not fast enough to react or have anything resembling half of a working brain.
    I'm a pretty good pitcher, but I'm not THAT good.
